At 1015, the automated weather observation facility (AWOS) located at AXH recorded, wind 
120 at 6 knots, 7 miles visibility, scattered clouds at 1,500 ft with a ceiling at 2,000 ft, 
temperature of 68 F, dew point 64 F, and an altimeter setting of 29.88 inches of mercury.
